[normal]4.0[bold]              [bold]BOIUK Strategic Priorities for the business in Northern Ireland[bold] 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]An intense focus on our customers and building long-term relationships that will help support the recovery of the Northern Ireland economy
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The 
[normal]provision of new lending to both consumers and businesses
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]A significant investment in the franchise’s distribution channels, quality of service and range of products. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.0[bold]              [bold]Banking with Bank of Ireland in Northern Ireland [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]An extensive network of 35 branches with a geographical spread across the region, complemen
[normal]ted by almost 200 onsite and retailer ATMS and an additional 28 with the PO.
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]A comprehensive suite of telephone, mobile and online banking services
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]A range of banking services provided to BOIUK customers via the PO. 
[normal]These include:
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Balance enquiries using
[normal] a BOIUK card and PIN
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Cash deposit with a BOIUK card or lodgement slip and same day value
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Cash withdrawals with a BOIUK card 
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Cheque deposit in an envelope. 
[normal]&#xa0;
